narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If you are a philosophy major, you absolutely MUST take a class with Della Rocca before graduating. If you aren't, then I would still highly recommend it. He is an amazing teacher and will really help you develop your own thoughts and work. This particular class onPersistence, Action and Relations, is absolutely worth taking if offered again. Whatever class you are taking, try to get Della Rocca to share his own views with you; they are compelling and pretty crazy and disturbing!
Yes, do take this class if you are interested in the material!!
